                <h1>Careers<br><hr></h1>
                    <div class="subnav">
                <p>
                            <a href="/about-us">
                                About Us
                            </a>
 | Careers                </p>
            </div>
                    <div class="whitePaper">
                <p><p class="text-center"><a href="http://jobs.esko.com/" target="_blank" class=" btn  btn-primary  btn-lg">Career Opportunities</a></p>
<p><img style="float: right; margin: 0px 0px 20px 20px; height: 308px; width: 600px;" alt="MediaBeacon USA office entry" src="/~/media/MBImages/MediaBeacon-Office.ashx?h=308&amp;w=600&amp;la=en&amp;hash=75A4A7F2D3A18135A34B0BD30EB1AA6EFF10FDA4" />MediaBeacon is an award-winning Enterprise Digital Asset Management (DAM) solutions provider. Our intuitive and highly personalized widget-based solutions allow organizations to find, organize, convert, track, and distribute digital media across the enterprise and globally. We help organizations manage their entire digital value chain by providing visibility, collaboration and analytics.</p>
<p>MediaBeacon is growing and we&rsquo;re excited about bringing on new talent. We believe that our employees are our most valuable asset, so we make every effort to reinvest in the comforts of our working environment and the health and well-being of our entire team. MediaBeacon offers the challenge, teamwork and opportunity of a startup combined with the stability of Danaher (NYSE: DHR) who generated 20.6 billion of revenue in 2015.</p>
<p>We are located on the top floor of the historic Colwell Building in the heart of the Minneapolis entertainment district with plenty of spots to eat, shop, and relax during lunch and after work. We are near Target Center, Target Field, Life Time Fitness, The Skyway, Minneapolis Central Library, the Hiawatha Line, Ramp C and multiple bus lines.</p>
<p>We have a unique, spacious and beautifully appointed office with natural light, ergonomic workstations that allow sitting or standing, a cafeteria with snacks and flexible hours</p>
<p>Other perks include company outings to the State Fair, company lunches, movie nights, triathlon teams, participation in local runs and other great events.</p>
<p>MediaBeacon, through Danaher, offers a comprehensive health &amp; wellness package, paid holidays, vacations and sick time, 401(k) with match, and partner discount programs.</p>
<p><br />
</p>
<p class="text-center"><a href="http://jobs.esko.com/" target="_blank" class=" btn  btn-primary  btn-lg">Career Opportunities</a></p></p>
